backlog
--------

- handle the mouse leaving the window mid-drag
	- push scroll
	- balsamiq follows you out of the window and keeps moving the items
	- it knows when you're above or below as you move around outside the window
- only show drag handles for directions you can drag in
- rectangle with the X through it that can be colour changed

- fancy arrows that actually "simple" SVG curves
  - xywh define the bounding rect where the SVG is drawn
  - start and end are independent %age co-ords inside the rect
  - needs two more drag handles to move the curve descriptors
  - clever drag mechanics to resize and re-position the box

- export view to get all the localstorage contents
  - needs a corresponding import
- groups of components
  - select one, select all - just need groups with their members described in the model
- export to clipboard as a PNG
  - everything
  - selected items
- text parsing e.g. this is *bold*, [hyperlink], {#ddd}color{#}
- change x/y in a clever way when pasting
- can you hook cut/copy/paste into the apple menu?
- insert a component from file ...
  - e.g. zatpark window, modal window
  - pagination as component
  - table tools (presets,filters,search,configure) as a component
  - remember recently used and include them in the adder dropdown
- drag without selecting first
- Cmd+R rects to account for scale
- selection tools e.g. Cmd+left/right to focus on a shape
- keyboard+drag to quickly add 
  - text with 't'
  - labels with 'l'
- lots of the little strings should be constants
- Elements need ...
  - reasonable declared widths
  - Redo the alignment features to consider the DOM elems which should all have correctly formed dimensions
  - Horizontal and vertical arrange features - space & distribute
- alignment guides
- inset guides
- inject version
- inject (c) date
- alias a field on the palette to change the label name e.g. {'bg': 'Colour'}

